### ─────────────────────────────
### DM THREADS
### ─────────────────────────────

### 5. Start DM thread (A → B)
POST {{chatUrl}}/chat/dm
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientId": "{{userBId}}"
}

###

@threadId = PASTE_THREAD_ID_HERE

### 6. Start same DM again — should return same thread (idempotent)
POST {{chatUrl}}/chat/dm
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientId": "{{userBId}}"
}

###

### 7. Try DM with yourself (should return 400)
POST {{chatUrl}}/chat/dm
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientId": "{{userAId}}"
}

###

### 8. Send message from A
POST {{chatUrl}}/chat/dm/{{threadId}}/message
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Hey neighbour, is the stray dog still near the park?"
}

###

### 9. Send reply from B
POST {{chatUrl}}/chat/dm/{{threadId}}/message
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Yes still there! Very friendly though."
}

###

### 10. Get message history
GET {{chatUrl}}/chat/dm/{{threadId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

###

### 11. Cursor pagination — paste nextCursor from response above
@cursor = PASTE_CURSOR_HERE
GET {{chatUrl}}/chat/dm/{{threadId}}/messages?cursor={{cursor}}&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

###

### 12. Mark thread as read
PATCH {{chatUrl}}/chat/dm/{{threadId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

###

### 13. List all DM threads
GET {{chatUrl}}/chat/threads
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

###

### 14. Try accessing thread you're not part of (should return 403)
### create a third user first, get their token, then try accessing this thread
POST {{chatUrl}}/chat/dm/{{threadId}}/message
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "I should not be able to post here if I am not a participant"
}


### ─────────────────────────────
### GROUP CHAT
### ─────────────────────────────

@communityId = a1b2c3d4-0000-0000-0000-000000000002

### 15. Get or create group thread
GET {{chatUrl}}/chat/group/{{communityId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

###

### 16. Send group message
POST {{chatUrl}}/chat/group/{{communityId}}/message
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Block cleanup this Saturday 10am, everyone welcome!"
}

###

### 17. Get group message history
GET {{chatUrl}}/chat/group/{{communityId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

###

### 18. Try accessing another community's group (should return 403)
GET {{chatUrl}}/chat/group/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000999
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}